			C4 & Requirement satisfaction gap@c4.html &  7 & 1
			C5 & Terminology divergence@c5.html       &  3 & 3
			C6 & Traceability disruption@c6.html      &  7 & 6
			C7 & Temporal skew@c7.html                &  3 & 9
